data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! This is an immaculate like-new townhouse! This Astin plan at Lakeview at Stonecrest has gorgeous hardwoods & 9' ft ceilings throughout. Modern kitchen boasts beautiful cabinetry, granite counters & island. Breakfast area flows effortlessly into the family room which is great for relaxation and entertainment. Spacious master suite is  spa-like bath w/ dual vanity & separate shower.  The other two bedrooms are a great size and won't disappoint! Privacy fence separates your yard from your neighbors. The pool & cabana is a fantastic amentity community! HOA is 155.00 and there are no rent restrictions.
